        "title": "Clean data before inserting to table",
        "body": "<p>I have my JPA  Entity something like below.<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>Employee{\n\nString name;\n\nString address;\n\nString phoneNumber;\n\nDate  joiningDate;\n\nboolean isActive;\n\n}\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>I am seeing that we have bad data inserted in the table for address,name like bad  characters  \\u000b which is new line character.I want to handle this generically to cleanse the data before inserting.\nI wanted to handle in dao layer because this gets called from many places hence want to handle at one central place.Some thing like AOP\nI am  doing <\/p>\n\n<pre><code>employeeDao.save(employee);\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>which then  does <code>employee.merge();<\/code><\/p>\n",
